column2: Game Night w/ Esn Bologna & Esn Trento

column6:
Hey guys!
Good news for everyoneee
This Thursday Esn Bologna and Esn Trento decided to organise together an online Game Night on Zoom! We have a lot of funny online games to present to you
We will be talking on Zoom and playing online multiplayer. There will also be a Speedfriendz room to get to know each other better!
Let’s meet virtually and have an amazing time
There will be fantastic gadgets from ESN Bologna for the winners !
